---
import { getInvolvedLink } from "../../content/get-involved-link";
---

<section class="w-full py-16">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary md:text-4xl">Get Involved</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-2 max-w-2xl text-lg font-semibold text-primary">
        Stay Engaged. Make an Impact.
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-primary/80">
      Join the MNPS Alumni Foundation and be part of a growing network of
      graduates who care about giving back and supporting the next generation.
      As a member, you'll receive updates on alumni events and stories, learn
      about local chapters, and find opportunities to mentor, volunteer, or
      invest in students.
    </p>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-primary/80">
      By joining, you help us build a robust alumni database that strengthens
      our collective voice. A strong network allows us to share timely updates,
      gather alumni feedback, spotlight achievements, and mobilize support for
      MNPS students and initiatives. When alumni are informed and engaged, we
      can advocate more effectively and create greater opportunities for the
      students who follow in our footsteps. Join the MNPS Alumni Network today!
    </p>
    <ul
      class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-3xl list-inside list-disc text-left text-base leading-relaxed text-primary/80"
    >
      <li>Provide crucial funds to support the scaling up of the foundation</li>
      <li>Gain access to exclusive alumni feedback activities</li>
      <li>Nominate standout alumni stories to be highlighted</li>
      <li>Help support MNPS initiatives and scholarships for graduates</li>
      <li>
        Receive our quarterly e-newsletter with the latest MNPS Alumni
        Foundation news
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <a
        href={getInvolvedLink}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-secondary/80"
      >
        GET INVOLVED
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
